Homepage: http://www.openmediavault.org

Package: openmediavault-usbbackup
Architecture: all
Depends: hdparm, rsync, openmediavault (>= 6.0)
Priority: optional
Description: openmediavault USB/eSATA backup plugin
 Automatically synchronise a shared folder to an USB/eSATA device and vice
 verse when it is plugged in.
 The device is put into sleep mode after synchronisation to signal that it
 can be removed safely.
